{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "0d95f1e5-3bea-469c-8367-0f5f27987fc6", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0d95f1e5-3bea-469c-8367-0f5f27987fc6@1.pkg/1772602412394/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602412620", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0d95f1e5-3bea-469c-8367-0f5f27987fc6@1.pkg/1772602412394/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602412620"}, "identifier": "0d95f1e5-3bea-469c-8367-0f5f27987fc6", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>七八岁</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><A id=\"_Hlk169710853\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\"></A><span>下列关于文章内容的理解有误的一项是（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "下列关于文章内容的理解有误的一项是（    ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0d95f1e5-3bea-469c-8367-0f5f27987fc6@1.pkg/item.json?v=1751869903248", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>寓言早在我国春秋战国时代就已经盛行，是民间口头创作。在先秦诸子百家的著作中，经常采用寓言阐明道理，《愚公移山》就是古代寓言中的名篇。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>我国古代称山南水北为阳，山北水南为阴。《愚公移山》中&ldquo;达于汉阴&rdquo;，即汉水南面。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>寓言《愚公移山》中，愚公对理想的坚持是热辣滚烫的。文章把愚公的&ldquo;愚&rdquo;与智叟的&ldquo;智&rdquo;进行对比，体现了愚公追求理想时不畏艰险、执著追求的精神。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;始龀&rdquo;代指小孩乳齿脱落长出恒齿的换牙时期，《愚公移山》中&ldquo;京城氏之孀妻有遗男，始龀&rdquo;，&ldquo;始龀&rdquo;，即六七岁。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><A id=\"_Hlk169710853\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\"></A><span>下列关于文章内容的理解有误的一项是（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db045